 intellectually enlightening, and often uncanny.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aArt and technology. 0aConceptual art. 0aMultimedia (Art) 0aMultimedia (Art). 0aMultimedia installations (Art) 0aMultimedia installations (Art). 7aART / General.2bisacsh  aconceptual art.  adigital convergence.  amedia specification.  amoving image.  astill image.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Chicago Press Complete eBook-Package 2018z97831106885800 cprintz978022650087440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226501062423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780226501062/original  a978-3-11-068858-0  University of Chicago Press Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aGBV-deGruyter-alles